Package: wikiliteApp
Title: Wikipedia History Flow — Interactive Shiny Application
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jonathan", "Sobel", email = "jsobel83@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for exploring Wikipedia article
    revision history, citation structure, editor behaviour, content stability,
    and vandalism patterns.  Implements an approximation of the Microsoft
    History Flow visualisation (Viégas, Wattenberg & Dave, CHI 2004) and
    provides tabs for authorship analysis, edit-war detection, citation
    latency, multi-article comparison networks, and category browsing.
    All data retrieval is handled by the 'wikilite' package
    <https://github.com/jsobel1/wikilite>.
